{
  "stem": "802.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my sister urinated into it because it was so bitter cold, and we had clogs, and the snow would get stuck, and the clogs were enormous.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were all one size.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you-- it was a kind of seesaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So as I said for the third time now, she urinated there, and she poured out the urine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, in this filth, in this-- this terrible place, the Germans made the kapos, the Jewish police, keep the grounds clean.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and it was January or February, so when she poured out the urine, it was yellow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so-- and so the Jewish policeman came to us, and he beat my mother-- he beat my sister for it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother said that her blood will not rest in the grave, as a result of which he saved me several times from selections.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my mother was a very brave woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we first arrived, there was a Jewish policeman who really wasn't nice, to say the least.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was beating some Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother screamed out to him, how could you, you, another Jew, do that?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ultimately, he was killed in Buchenwald by-- you know, as-- as revenge-- not revenge-- punishment, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were not too many, but there were some who-- and I have no pity for them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- and I make no apologies for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After all, we're entitled to-- to awful people, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although perhaps it's not the most moral thing to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody should be perfect.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I guess we are not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we were sent to another camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh no, in this camp, there was no soap.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
